<div class="contentdiv clearfix"><div class="clearfix"><h2>What students have to say</h2>
<div class="leftFloat"><p class="largeType">"See, the difference between college and high school is how you get help. In college, you have to ask for it and look for help yourself. In high school, you don't even have to ask because they know you need help in some classes. Students need to understand that people aren't just going to come to you."<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;--Shannon
</p></div><div class="rightFloat"><img src="/modules/mod_hs_coll/images/shannon.jpg" alt="Shannon" width="295" height="221" />
